Authentic Chinese restaurant with great Cantonese style dim sum. If you are expecting traditional service like that in an American restaurant, please do not bother. If you are adventurous, sit down and pick what you like off the cart full of delicious dim sum that passes by your table. The girls there are very kind but they don't speak very good English. So be patient with them and they will try to help you choosing your plate.
